Sharks do exist, but they rarely attack people. Most sharks fear humans and they will swim away from them.
Saltwater crocodiles do not actively live in the sea. Their main habitat is estuaries north of Rockhampton.
Early reservation gives travelers peace of mind that they will have a room upon arriving at their destination.
Travel agents often have agreements with specific hotels, but you may be able to book other types of accommodations through such agents, such as campsites.
Travel agents generally offer plans that include breakfast, transportation arrangements to and from the airport, or even combined plans with flights and hotels.
They can also hold your reservation, if you need time to consider the proposal or obtain other documents for the intended location (for example, a visa).
All changes or requests must be directed first to the travel agent and not directly to the hotel.
